
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zeilenga-ldap-incr-01.txt'>
    <title>"LDAP Modify-Increment Extension", Kurt Zeilenga</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zeilenga-ldap-incr-01.txt</link>
    <description>This document describes an extension to the Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP) Modify operation to support an increment capability. This extension is useful in provisioning applications, especially when combined with the assertion control and/or the pre-read or post-read control extension.</description>
    <dc:date>2005-02-14T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
